# This file is INTENTIONALLY NOT SYMLINKED to ~/.ssh/allowed_signers.
# The reason: home/git/install.bash auto-generates the live file from
# `git config user.email` + ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub on each new machine.
# A symlink here would prevent regeneration with the correct (work
# vs personal) email on the new machine.
#
# Treat this as a backup of all known signing identities for cross-
# referencing if the live file is ever lost or corrupted.
#
# Format: <principal-spec> <key-type> <base64-key> [<comment>]
# Reference: man ssh-keygen, "ALLOWED SIGNERS"

